<para style="p">

  <verse number="4" style="v" />Rejoice in the Lord always. Again I will say, rejoice.

  <verse number="5" style="v" />Let your gentleness be known to all people. The Lord is near.

  <verse number="6" style="v" />Do not be anxious about anything. Instead, in everything by prayer and requests, with thanksgiving, let your requests be known to God.

  <verse number="7" style="v" />And the peace of God, which exceeds all understanding, will guard your hearts and your thoughts in Christ Jesus.</para>

